</header>
<span class="meta-info">Friday, November 17, 2017</span>
<div class="post-body">
<p>Click on the picture below as Roco Chief Instructor Brad Warr discusses&nbsp;recent training&nbsp;at the North Dakota Safety Council's new confined space rescue training prop. </p>
