<a href="http://www.kfyrtv.com/content/news/New-facility-give-rescues-workers-a-place-to-train-457855363.html"><img alt="" style="border: 0px solid; width: 540px; height: 270px; vertical-align: middle;" src="/ALL BLOG IMAGES/BWarr.png" /></a>
