<h3><a href="/roco-rescue-blog/industrial-rescue-i-ii-class-nov-13-17-at-ndsc" title="NDSC to Host Roco Rescue Training">NDSC to Host Roco Rescue Training</a></h3>
</header>
<span class="meta-info">Tuesday, October 17, 2017</span>
<div class="post-body">
<p><a href="/_literature_240059/NDSC"><img alt="" src="/ALL BLOG IMAGES/ND Industrial Rescue Sell Sheet low res.jpg" style="border: 0px solid; float: left; width: 240px; height: 311px; margin-right: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px;" /></a>Join us in Bismarck, ND, for Roco&rsquo;s Industrial I/II course at the Safety Council&rsquo;s new training facility. The NDSC has an indoor confined space rescue prop designed with input from Roco Rescue. <a href="/LiteratureRetrieve.aspx?ID=240059">Click here</a> (or the picture) to download the flyer information.</p>
<p>This course is for industrial and municipal rescuers who handle confined space and high angle rescues in industrial environments. Course dates are November 13-17, 2017. </p>
<p>Call the NDSC at 800-932-8890 for more information; or contact Roco at 800-647-7626. We will also be conducting additional Roco courses at the NDSC in 2018.</p>
